11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 17-107B of Title 11, unless
14 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 There is hereby re-created in the State Treasury a revolving
16 fund for the State Auditor and Inspector to be designated the
17 "Special Investigative Unit Auditing Revolving Fund". The fund
18 shall be a continuing fund, not subject to fiscal year limitations,
19 and shall consist of all monies received by the State Auditor and
20 Inspector from funds withheld from a municipality's allocations of
21 gasoline taxes as provided in Section 17-107 of Title 11 of the
22 Oklahoma Statutes, all monies received from legislative
23 appropriations for the purpose of conducting investigative municipal
24 audits, and all monies that remain in the Special Investigative Unit
